{"tid":1968692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"檢疫令 7/5  屆満， 9/5 縱橫遊 支那華東遊成團","createTime":"2020-04-11T23:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T02:33:50.000Z","uid":36494,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"843d110b82cc3f2207411df46d544ab137baa86b","tid":1968692,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T23:59:29.000Z","msg":"明報頭條搶先睇<br />\n<br />\n【蠢蠢欲動】<span style=\"color: red;\">政府對由內地抵港人士實施強制檢疫令，有效期至5月7日，旅行社縱橫遊昨宣布，首個內地團將於5月9日出發，屬華東五天團，</span>團費低至99元，相當於SARS疫後價一成，形容屬「蝕住做」推廣，已有約10人報名，包括小童，並已成團；而5月其他日子另有華東團或北京團開放報名，收費亦低至99元，昨收到逾40個查詢。衛生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，希望市民勿掉以輕心，不要外遊。有傳染病醫生再三提醒，決定外遊者要承擔潛在風險，高危人士現不宜外遊&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n#明報 #明報即時新聞 #新冠肺炎 #抗疫新階段 #檢疫令 #恢復外遊 #縱橫遊 #華東團 #內地團<br />\n<br />\n==========================<br />\n【讚好「明報即時新聞」專頁】<br />\n● 請於fb將專頁設定為「搶先看」（See First）<br />\n● 請下載「明報」App，緊貼最新消息：<br />\niPhone：<a href=\"http://apple.co/1foEZKS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F1foEZKS&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=d883faf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://apple.co/1foEZKS</a><br />\nAndroid：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/1foESyU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1foESyU&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=126ab154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1foESyU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYFW4VV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYFW4VV.jpg&h=84e8c360&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1c815c031947f105f42cb782265a5853323a5ad","tid":1968692,"uid":123774,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:01:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>縱橫遊係香港700萬人公敵</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3e8e8abfa74800a3ce36db037ef509a63bcdf45b","tid":1968692,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:07:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b9